    <preface>
      <longTitle>
        <p><docTitle>Senado Plenary Session: Review of the Valencian Paella Reform</docTitle></p>
      </longTitle>
      <p>Session of June 20, 2024 of the Senado de Gastronomia.</p>
      <p>Agenda: Review of the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Paella Reform Bill</ref> approved by the Camara de Ingredientes.</p>
    </preface>

    <debateBody>
      <debateSection eId="dbsect_apertura" name="opening">
        <heading>Opening of the session</heading>
        <speech eId="speech_1" by="#presidente">
          <from>President Fernandez</from>
          <p>The Senado session is called to order. We have received the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Paella Reform Bill</ref> from the Camara de Ingredientes via <ref href="/akn/poc/communication/camara-to-senado">official communication</ref>. The floor is open for deliberation.</p>
        </speech>
      </debateSection>

      <debateSection eId="dbsect_debate" name="debate">
        <heading>Senate deliberation</heading>
        <speech eId="speech_2" by="#sen-tokio">
          <from>Sen. Tokio</from>
          <p>Honorable President, while I support modernizing our food standards, I believe the rice flexibility goes too far. As someone working on <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/sushi-rice-regulation">sushi rice regulation</ref>, I understand that rice variety is fundamental to a dish's identity.</p>
          <p>I propose we support the bill but urge the Supreme Court to review the rice provisions.</p>
        </speech>

        <speech eId="speech_3" by="#sen-tradition">
          <from>Sen. Tradition</from>
          <p>I echo the concerns of my colleague. The Senado has a duty to protect our gastronomic heritage while allowing for reasonable evolution. The 'mixed paella' distinction is wise, but bomba rice must remain sacred for the Valencian designation.</p>
        </speech>
      </debateSection>

      <debateSection eId="dbsect_votacion" name="voting">
        <heading>Voting</heading>
        <speech eId="speech_4" by="#presidente">
          <from>President Fernandez</from>
          <p>The Senado approves the bill with a recommendation to review rice provisions. The bill will proceed to promulgation. The session is adjourned.</p>
        </speech>
      </debateSection>
